      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "High-level Compute (Linux)\n\nJetson Orin Nano Super\n- autonomy / vision / mapping\n- outer-loop control (e.g., MPC\nsetpoints @ 20–50 Hz)\n- logging + plots\n- SSH development",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 16,
      "containerId": "1a089b84899842be",
      "originalText": "High-level Compute (Linux)\n\nJetson Orin Nano Super\n- autonomy / vision / mapping\n- outer-loop control (e.g., MPC setpoints @ 20–50 Hz)\n- logging + plots\n- SSH development",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a6",
      "frameId": "573a113a90a44907",
      "autoResize": true
