      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Real-time Controller (Reflexes)\n\nSTM32 NUCLEO-F446RE\n- inner loop balance @ 500–1000 Hz\n- reads IMU + encoders\n- runs PID/LQR/observer\n- outputs motor commands",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 16,
      "containerId": "362dac728b5e4635",
      "originalText": "Real-time Controller (Reflexes)\n\nSTM32 NUCLEO-F446RE\n- inner loop balance @ 500–1000 Hz\n- reads IMU + encoders\n- runs PID/LQR/observer\n- outputs motor commands",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a8",
      "frameId": "573a113a90a44907",
      "autoResize": true
    },
